snippet.title: Gigantic Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
A team action game developed by Seattle-area studio Motiga, where heroes battle alongside a massive guardian in a fight for supremacy. Join the fight and be one of the first to try Gigantic!

Learn more at: http://www.gogigantic.com
Like: https://www.facebook.com/GoGigantic
Follow: https://twitter.com/GoGigantic
Watch: http://www.twitch.tv/gogigantic
